      <title>BSP州长说，菲律宾可以抵抗比索的大波动。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/php-usd-philippines-to-resist-large-swings-in-peso-central-bank-governor-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[州长埃利·雷莫洛纳（Eli Remolona）表示，菲律宾中央银行将抵抗比索的大幅波动，尤其是如果它正在削弱，埃利·雷莫洛纳（Eli Remolona）表示，从印度尼西亚到土耳其的新兴市场本周变动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/php-usd-philippines-to-resist-large-swings-in-peso-central-bank-governor-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 03:07:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
